@startuml architecture
title DeckMux — Package Architecture

skinparam backgroundColor #ffffff
skinparam defaultFontColor #333333
skinparam componentBorderColor #d1d5db
skinparam componentBackgroundColor #f3f4f6
skinparam packageBorderColor #d1d5db
skinparam packageBackgroundColor #ffffff
skinparam arrowColor #2563eb
skinparam noteBorderColor #d1d5db
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #f9fafb

package "undef-terminal-deckmux (standalone)" {
  [_protocol.py\nmessage types & serialization] as PROTO
  [_presence.py\nPresenceStore + UserPresence] as PRESENCE
  [_names.py\nname & color generation] as NAMES
  [_transfer.py\nTransferManager + keystroke queue] as XFER
  [_edge.py\nviewport math] as EDGE
}

package "undef-terminal (integration)" {
  [deckmux/_hub_mixin.py\nTermHub integration] as MIX
  [hijack/hub/core.py\nTermHub] as HUB
  [hijack/routes/websockets.py\nmessage routing] as WS
}

package "undef-terminal-frontend" {
  [deckmux/deckmux.ts\ncoordinator] as COORD
  [deckmux/presence-bar.ts\navatar bar] as BAR
  [deckmux/edge-indicators.ts\nminimap bars] as EDGE_UI
  [deckmux/cursor-overlay.ts\npins + selections] as CURSOR
  [deckmux/control-panel.ts\ntoasts + menus] as CTRL
}

MIX --> PROTO : uses
MIX --> PRESENCE : uses
MIX --> NAMES : uses
MIX --> XFER : uses
MIX --> EDGE : uses
MIX --> HUB : mixin
WS --> MIX : routes presence msgs

COORD --> BAR
COORD --> EDGE_UI
COORD --> CURSOR
COORD --> CTRL

note right of PROTO : Zero dependencies\nStandalone package
note right of MIX : Extends TermHub\nvia mixin pattern

@enduml
